{"title":"Projects","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Projects","subtitle":"Independent work at the intersection of data, law, and applied research","toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n::: {.project-grid}\n\n::: {.project-card}\n<span class=\"project-card-tag\" style=\"background:#e8f0fe; color:#1a56db;\">Data Storytelling</span>\n<p class=\"project-card-title\">The Hip-Hop Periodic Table</p>\n<p class=\"project-card-desc\">\n  A multidimensional dataset of 139 hip-hop artists scored across five independently\n  defined lyricism dimensions with documented confidence flags, a formal data dictionary,\n  and a source bibliography. Built as a teaching artifact for professional/executive\n  education in measurement design and data storytelling.\n</p>\n<div class=\"project-card-meta\">\n  <span><span class=\"project-card-accent\" style=\"background:#4472C4;\"></span>R · Quarto · Excel</span>\n  <span><span class=\"project-card-accent\" style=\"background:#41ab5d;\"></span>139 artists · 6 eras</span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<a href=\"../hiphop/hiphop_dashboard.html\" style=\"font-weight:600; color:#2E75B6;\">\n  Open dashboard →\n</a>\n:::\n\n::: {.project-card}\n<span class=\"project-card-tag\" style=\"background:#fef3c7; color:#92400e;\">Coming Soon</span>\n<p class=\"project-card-title\">Project Two Title</p>\n<p class=\"project-card-desc\">\n  A short description of your next project. What question does it ask?\n  What data does it use? What should a reader expect to learn?\n</p>\n<div class=\"project-card-meta\">\n  <span>Tools / methods</span>\n</div>\n:::\n\n::: {.project-card}\n<span class=\"project-card-tag\" style=\"background:#fef3c7; color:#92400e;\">Coming Soon</span>\n<p class=\"project-card-title\">Project Three Title</p>\n<p class=\"project-card-desc\">\n  Another project placeholder. Delete this card or replace it when ready.\n</p>\n<div class=\"project-card-meta\">\n  <span>Tools / methods</span>\n</div>\n:::\n\n:::\n\n---\n\n::: {.callout-note}\nAll data